00:01:47.028 --> 00:01:48.320 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: How did that happen?

00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:49.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Yeah, how did
this happen for you?

00:01:49.850 --> 00:01:51.308 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Well,
