00:18:58.650 --> 00:19:00.960 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: I know that.

00:19:00.960 --> 00:19:05.070 align:middle line:84%
And so let's say you're
listening to "Coast to Coast

00:19:05.070 --> 00:19:09.413 align:middle line:84%
AM," but it's broadcast on an
FM station in certain markets.

00:19:09.413 --> 00:19:10.330 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That happens.

00:19:10.330 --> 00:19:11.130 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: So, see?

00:19:11.130 --> 00:19:12.540 align:middle line:90%
The frequencies overlap.

00:19:12.540 --> 00:19:17.070 align:middle line:84%
And that's exactly it, is that
Albert Einstein was correct,

00:19:17.070 --> 00:19:19.920 align:middle line:84%
as Uri Geller said,
that there is no matter.

00:19:19.920 --> 00:19:21.600 align:middle line:84%
There's just energy
which vibrates

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:22.740 align:middle line:90%
at different frequencies.

00:19:22.740 --> 00:19:25.800 align:middle line:84%
And also, Uri was
quoting, I believe

00:19:25.800 --> 00:19:27.660 align:middle line:84%
it's the second law
of thermodynamics,

00:19:27.660 --> 00:19:30.420 align:middle line:84%
that energy can neither
be created nor destroyed,

00:19:30.420 --> 00:19:32.880 align:middle line:84%
only transferred from
one form to another.

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.320 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's correct.

00:19:34.320 --> 00:19:35.970 align:middle line:90%
And it moves on.

00:19:35.970 --> 00:19:38.810 align:middle line:10%
Now what are the ghosts?

00:19:38.810 --> 00:19:42.320 align:middle line:84%
When he mentioned ghosts,
we all believe in ghosts--

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:43.610 align:middle line:90%
what's happening with that?

00:19:43.610 --> 00:19:45.240 align:middle line:90%
This is energy coming back?

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:46.748 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:19:46.748 --> 00:19:48.790 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Well, there's
three schools of thought

00:19:48.790 --> 00:19:51.520 align:middle line:90%
on what a ghost is.

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:56.080 align:middle line:84%
One is that it's a
spirit that immediately

00:19:56.080 --> 00:19:57.970 align:middle line:84%
transfers to the
other side, and that's

00:19:57.970 --> 00:19:59.950 align:middle line:90%
the school I subscribe to.

00:19:59.950 --> 00:20:02.800 align:middle line:84%
Then there are people who
feel that ghosts are somehow

00:20:02.800 --> 00:20:06.010 align:middle line:90%
trapped here, ergo hauntings.

00:20:06.010 --> 00:20:08.860 align:middle line:84%
I don't necessarily
subscribe to that theory.

00:20:08.860 --> 00:20:12.010 align:middle line:84%
And the third is
that a place that

00:20:12.010 --> 00:20:16.330 align:middle line:84%
is haunted or very strong
with the force, if you will,

00:20:16.330 --> 00:20:19.430 align:middle line:84%
is actually a
residual energy echo.

00:20:19.430 --> 00:20:23.140 align:middle line:84%
In other words, if you
go to a place that's--

00:20:23.140 --> 00:20:26.890 align:middle line:84%
well, from my own
experience, when I went

00:20:26.890 --> 00:20:29.020 align:middle line:90%
to Dachau Concentration Camp.

00:20:29.020 --> 00:20:31.420 align:middle line:84%
When I was 19, I was
visiting Germany,

00:20:31.420 --> 00:20:33.700 align:middle line:84%
and I was with a bunch
of college friends,

00:20:33.700 --> 00:20:35.180 align:middle line:90%
and we're a bit hung over.

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:35.980 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:20:35.980 --> 00:20:38.350 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: And I wasn't
prepared for what happened.

00:20:38.350 --> 00:20:40.487 align:middle line:84%
And when I walked into the
concentration camp, all

00:20:40.487 --> 00:20:42.070 align:middle line:84%
of a sudden, I found
myself surrounded

00:20:42.070 --> 00:20:43.270 align:middle line:90%
by all these shrieking spirits.

00:20:43.270 --> 00:20:44.410 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You could feel it.

00:20:44.410 --> 00:20:46.243 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: And I could
see the striped garb.

00:20:46.243 --> 00:20:49.960 align:middle line:84%
And I remember, I collapsed on
my knees, and I was shaking.

00:20:49.960 --> 00:20:52.420 align:middle line:84%
And one of my friends,
he was from my hometown,

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:54.400 align:middle line:84%
and he kind of knew
about my family and all

00:20:54.400 --> 00:20:55.210 align:middle line:84%
that, and he goes,
all right, buddy,

00:20:55.210 --> 00:20:56.293 align:middle line:90%
we're getting out of here.

00:20:56.293 --> 00:20:58.210 align:middle line:84%
And he just pulled me
up and got me on a bus.

00:20:58.210 --> 00:21:00.210 align:middle line:84%
He goes, look, dude, I
don't know what happened,

00:21:00.210 --> 00:21:02.270 align:middle line:90%
but something happened.

00:21:02.270 --> 00:21:04.880 align:middle line:84%
I don't believe that those
spirits are trapped there.

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:08.690 align:middle line:10%
But when something intensely
traumatic happens in an area,

00:21:08.690 --> 00:21:10.970 align:middle line:10%
it creates an energy echo.

00:21:10.970 --> 00:21:13.250 align:middle line:84%
So it's no more
a sentient spirit

00:21:13.250 --> 00:21:16.340 align:middle line:84%
than your reflection
in a mirror is you.

00:21:16.340 --> 00:21:19.400 align:middle line:84%
And that's why people that
do clearings, or exorcisms,

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:22.130 align:middle line:84%
or whatever, of a
particular place,

00:21:22.130 --> 00:21:24.500 align:middle line:84%
they're essentially
breaking that echo,

00:21:24.500 --> 00:21:26.450 align:middle line:90%
deflecting the energy off.

00:21:26.450 --> 00:21:30.050 align:middle line:84%
Because based on the thousands
of readings I've done--

00:21:30.050 --> 00:21:31.520 align:middle line:84%
George, at this
point in my life,

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:34.980 align:middle line:84%
I've done readings for
over 15,000 people.

00:21:34.980 --> 00:21:38.840 align:middle line:84%
And in each reading,
particularly the one-on-ones,

00:21:38.840 --> 00:21:42.620 align:middle line:84%
at least six to seven
spirits per person

00:21:42.620 --> 00:21:44.623 align:middle line:84%
comes through, oftentimes,
more than that.

00:21:44.623 --> 00:21:45.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's a lot.

00:21:45.540 --> 00:21:48.590 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Yeah, so maybe
100,000, 200,000 spirits

00:21:48.590 --> 00:21:50.090 align:middle line:90%
I've communicated with.

00:21:50.090 --> 00:21:54.500 align:middle line:84%
They know full well, the second
they are done with this body,

00:21:54.500 --> 00:21:58.430 align:middle line:84%
they revert to a purely
energetic eternal state,

00:21:58.430 --> 00:21:59.450 align:middle line:90%
and they're aware of it.

00:21:59.450 --> 00:22:01.920 align:middle line:84%
That's why I don't believe
ghosts are trapped here.

00:22:01.920 --> 00:22:05.170 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What is the
electromagnetic soul, the EMS?

00:22:05.170 --> 00:22:07.440 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: Yes, the EMS.

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:10.420 align:middle line:90%
We are eternal consciousness.

00:22:10.420 --> 00:22:15.750 align:middle line:84%
And if you look at all the great
spiritual teachers from Krishna

00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:21.720 align:middle line:84%
through Moses, Buddha,
Jesus, Muhammad, Yogananda

00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:24.210 align:middle line:84%
Paramahansa, Saint
Francis of Assisi,

00:22:24.210 --> 00:22:28.410 align:middle line:84%
the Native American teachers,
all the great belief systems

00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:30.000 align:middle line:90%
teach us that the soul--

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:33.660 align:middle line:84%
who and what we are-- pre-exist
the body, comes into the body,

00:22:33.660 --> 00:22:36.630 align:middle line:90%
moves on after the body dies.

00:22:36.630 --> 00:22:38.310 align:middle line:84%
And like we were
just discussing,

00:22:38.310 --> 00:22:40.770 align:middle line:84%
energy is neither
created nor destroyed,

00:22:40.770 --> 00:22:43.900 align:middle line:84%
only transferred from
one form to another.

00:22:43.900 --> 00:22:48.030 align:middle line:84%
So based on my research,
I developed the term

00:22:48.030 --> 00:22:52.110 align:middle line:84%
the electromagnetic soul to
describe who and what we really

00:22:52.110 --> 00:22:55.800 align:middle line:84%
are, which is pure
consciousness, which is

00:22:55.800 --> 00:22:57.788 align:middle line:90%
eternal electromagnetic energy.

00:22:57.788 --> 00:22:58.830 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's all energy.

00:22:58.830 --> 00:23:01.440 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Ergo the
electromagnetic soul.

00:23:01.440 --> 00:23:03.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Which is
terminal lucidity.

00:23:03.300 --> 00:23:04.320 align:middle line:90%
What is that?

00:23:04.320 --> 00:23:07.020 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Terminal
lucidity occurs in about 10%

00:23:07.020 --> 00:23:11.340 align:middle line:84%
of the cases, where somebody is
completely nonresponsive prior

00:23:11.340 --> 00:23:15.240 align:middle line:84%
to death, could be due to
brain damage, Alzheimer's,

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:17.190 align:middle line:90%
meningitis strokes.

00:23:17.190 --> 00:23:20.530 align:middle line:84%
They are not responsive at
all, and their condition

00:23:20.530 --> 00:23:21.330 align:middle line:90%
is terminal.

00:23:21.330 --> 00:23:24.090 align:middle line:84%
And then right before
they die, George,

00:23:24.090 --> 00:23:27.120 align:middle line:84%
usually in the last few
minutes, they wake up,

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:30.090 align:middle line:84%
and they recognize
people around them.

00:23:30.090 --> 00:23:31.870 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And things
and stuff like that.

00:23:31.870 --> 00:23:32.787 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: And things.

00:23:32.787 --> 00:23:35.550 align:middle line:84%
And they're completely
lucid and coherent.

00:23:35.550 --> 00:23:38.970 align:middle line:84%
And this term,
terminal lucidity,

00:23:38.970 --> 00:23:44.470 align:middle line:84%
was developed by Michael Nahm,
who's a German neurobiologist.

00:23:44.470 --> 00:23:48.490 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I have always thought
about the deathbed discussion

00:23:48.490 --> 00:23:51.520 align:middle line:90%
of Steven Jobs, Apple Computer.

00:23:51.520 --> 00:23:55.850 align:middle line:10%
And his last words were
like, oh, wow, oh, wow.

00:23:55.850 --> 00:23:56.650 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: Yes.

00:23:56.650 --> 00:23:58.060 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, wow.

00:23:58.060 --> 00:24:02.410 align:middle line:84%
Sam Kinison, the comedian
who died in a tragic car

00:24:02.410 --> 00:24:07.810 align:middle line:84%
crash going back between LA and
Vegas, was petrified of dying

00:24:07.810 --> 00:24:08.870 align:middle line:90%
and didn't want to die.

00:24:08.870 --> 00:24:12.230 align:middle line:84%
But right at the
moment of death,

00:24:12.230 --> 00:24:17.840 align:middle line:84%
in front of eyewitnesses, he
went, oh, OK, OK, and died.

00:24:17.840 --> 00:24:18.890 align:middle line:90%
What is that?

00:24:18.890 --> 00:24:21.530 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: That's known
as a deathbed vision.

00:24:21.530 --> 00:24:26.840 align:middle line:84%
And a deathbed vision is when
somebody who is actively dying,

00:24:26.840 --> 00:24:28.790 align:middle line:84%
all of a sudden,
their frequency aligns

00:24:28.790 --> 00:24:30.860 align:middle line:84%
with the frequency
of the other side,

00:24:30.860 --> 00:24:34.310 align:middle line:84%
and they're able to
perceive spirits.

00:24:34.310 --> 00:24:35.660 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's real, isn't it?

00:24:35.660 --> 00:24:36.577 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: It is real.

00:24:36.577 --> 00:24:38.600 align:middle line:84%
The scientists who
study this, George,

00:24:38.600 --> 00:24:41.210 align:middle line:84%
they are convinced that
it's not a hallucination.

00:24:41.210 --> 00:24:44.240 align:middle line:84%
I, myself, have observed this
on a number of occasions.

00:24:44.240 --> 00:24:46.400 align:middle line:84%
Because in my
capacity as a medium,

00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:49.760 align:middle line:84%
I'm often called to the bedside
of people who are dying.

00:24:49.760 --> 00:24:52.190 align:middle line:90%
And I can assure you it is real.

00:24:52.190 --> 00:24:53.928 align:middle line:84%
They are actually
seeing the spirits

00:24:53.928 --> 00:24:55.220 align:middle line:90%
who are coming to welcome them.

00:24:55.220 --> 00:24:57.260 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Not a
hallucination by any means.

00:24:57.260 --> 00:24:58.802 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: It is
not a hallucination.

00:24:58.802 --> 00:25:00.410 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Near-death
experiences--

00:25:00.410 --> 00:25:02.130 align:middle line:90%
we have heard lots of them.

00:25:02.130 --> 00:25:03.130 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: Yes, we have.

00:25:03.130 --> 00:25:04.730 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Eben
Alexander, the things

00:25:04.730 --> 00:25:06.830 align:middle line:90%
that Raymond Moody talks about.

00:25:06.830 --> 00:25:08.068 align:middle line:90%
What's your take on those?

00:25:08.068 --> 00:25:09.860 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Near-death
experiences are real.

00:25:09.860 --> 00:25:11.670 align:middle line:84%
I had one when I
was four years old.

00:25:11.670 --> 00:25:12.020 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You did?

00:25:12.020 --> 00:25:12.820 align:middle line:90%
What happened?

00:25:12.820 --> 00:25:14.000 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: I did.

00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:15.530 align:middle line:84%
It's a fairly lengthy
story, so I'll

00:25:15.530 --> 00:25:16.610 align:middle line:90%
give you the condensed version.

00:25:16.610 --> 00:25:18.110 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Give me
the Cliff version.

00:25:18.110 --> 00:25:19.580 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: The CliffNotes.

00:25:19.580 --> 00:25:23.660 align:middle line:84%
I had a real bad blood
infection from impetigo, called

00:25:23.660 --> 00:25:27.710 align:middle line:84%
septicemia, and I went into
cardiopulmonary failure.

00:25:27.710 --> 00:25:28.580 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh my god.

00:25:28.580 --> 00:25:30.350 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: And my
mother was frantic.

00:25:30.350 --> 00:25:33.770 align:middle line:84%
And she ran outside and started
screaming, my baby's dying.

00:25:33.770 --> 00:25:36.440 align:middle line:84%
And our neighbor just
happened to be a fireman,

00:25:36.440 --> 00:25:38.390 align:middle line:84%
and he runs across the
street, starts doing--

00:25:38.390 --> 00:25:39.200 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He pumped you.

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:41.075 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Yeah, he
starts doing compressions

00:25:41.075 --> 00:25:44.480 align:middle line:84%
just as an ambulance pulls
up, because my sister called

00:25:44.480 --> 00:25:45.560 align:middle line:90%
an ambulance.

00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:48.890 align:middle line:84%
On the way to the hospital,
they slammed the door,

00:25:48.890 --> 00:25:51.230 align:middle line:84%
and the ventilator hose
got caught in the door,

00:25:51.230 --> 00:25:56.100 align:middle line:84%
so then I stopped breathing,
and I went into cardiac arrest.

00:25:56.100 --> 00:25:58.340 align:middle line:84%
And so my mother was in
the ambulance with them,

00:25:58.340 --> 00:26:00.580 align:middle line:84%
and they said, we've
got to get this open.

00:26:00.580 --> 00:26:01.850 align:middle line:90%
And she said, I'll do it.

00:26:01.850 --> 00:26:06.050 align:middle line:84%
So the paramedic's holding
onto the gurney that I'm on.

00:26:06.050 --> 00:26:07.688 align:middle line:84%
He's holding onto
my mom's waistband.

00:26:07.688 --> 00:26:09.980 align:middle line:84%
She pries the door of the
ambulance open, gets her foot

00:26:09.980 --> 00:26:10.700 align:middle line:90%
and yanks it in.

00:26:10.700 --> 00:26:11.500 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Gets the--

00:26:11.500 --> 00:26:13.850 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: And meanwhile,
I get catapulted out

00:26:13.850 --> 00:26:15.950 align:middle line:90%
of the ambulance.

00:26:15.950 --> 00:26:18.690 align:middle line:84%
I'm seeing it going
down the highway.

00:26:18.690 --> 00:26:22.220 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, I go
into this bright white light,

00:26:22.220 --> 00:26:25.520 align:middle line:90%
and there's these people there.

00:26:25.520 --> 00:26:29.450 align:middle line:84%
And the thing is, George,
the looked translucent,

00:26:29.450 --> 00:26:32.450 align:middle line:90%
like a clear version of people.

00:26:32.450 --> 00:26:34.250 align:middle line:84%
And they glowed
from the inside out.

00:26:34.250 --> 00:26:36.350 align:middle line:90%
And they were really nice to me.

00:26:36.350 --> 00:26:38.390 align:middle line:90%
And I wasn't afraid of them.

00:26:38.390 --> 00:26:42.410 align:middle line:84%
And then they said, you're
going to be OK, Mark.

00:26:42.410 --> 00:26:43.340 align:middle line:90%
You're going to be OK.

00:26:43.340 --> 00:26:48.120 align:middle line:84%
And then I heard and saw
an even brighter light.

00:26:48.120 --> 00:26:52.580 align:middle line:84%
And I heard the words,
"eternal light, eternal life."

00:26:52.580 --> 00:26:55.550 align:middle line:84%
Then I hear, "clear," and
I'm back in the ambulance

00:26:55.550 --> 00:26:57.383 align:middle line:84%
because they hit me
with defibrillator pads,

00:26:57.383 --> 00:26:59.550 align:middle line:84%
and they shocked me, I
guess, out of the other side.

00:26:59.550 --> 00:27:01.040 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Jarring
feeling, isn't it?

00:27:01.040 --> 00:27:01.840 align:middle line:90%
>>ANTHONY: It was.

00:27:01.840 --> 00:27:05.120 align:middle line:84%
And later in the hospital,
they were hitting me

00:27:05.120 --> 00:27:07.520 align:middle line:90%
with heavy duty IV antibiotics.

00:27:07.520 --> 00:27:10.010 align:middle line:84%
And when I came out of
it, I remember asking

00:27:10.010 --> 00:27:12.238 align:middle line:90%
my parents, what is eternal?

00:27:12.238 --> 00:27:14.280 align:middle line:84%
And I remember mom and
dad looking at each other.

00:27:14.280 --> 00:27:16.400 align:middle line:84%
And what I didn't
realize, at that point,

00:27:16.400 --> 00:27:19.460 align:middle line:84%
my dad, years
before, had not one

00:27:19.460 --> 00:27:21.457 align:middle line:90%
but two near-death experiences.

00:27:21.457 --> 00:27:22.790 align:middle line:90%
And then when I was a teenager--

00:27:22.790 --> 00:27:24.457 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So they knew
what was going on.

00:27:24.457 --> 00:27:27.690 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: Yeah, this has
been part of my family.

00:27:27.690 --> 00:27:31.640 align:middle line:84%
And so what happens is in an
NDE, a near-death experience,

00:27:31.640 --> 00:27:34.580 align:middle line:84%
your electromagnetic
soul leaves your body,

00:27:34.580 --> 00:27:37.380 align:middle line:84%
and it touches that higher
frequency of the other side.

00:27:37.380 --> 00:27:38.180 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Right.

00:27:38.180 --> 00:27:39.560 align:middle line:84%
>>ANTHONY: And
you will encounter

00:27:39.560 --> 00:27:42.090 align:middle line:84%
deceased loved ones,
the divine power,

00:27:42.090 --> 00:27:47.510 align:middle line:84%
dare I say the word "God,"
and then you return.

00:27:47.510 --> 00:27:50.370 align:middle line:84%
And since the dawn
of recorded history,

00:27:50.370 --> 00:27:52.910 align:middle line:84%
there have been accounts
of these resurrections,

00:27:52.910 --> 00:27:57.050 align:middle line:84%
where people who died and then
came back to tell about it.

00:27:57.050 --> 00:27:59.840 align:middle line:84%
Hippocrates in Ancient
Greece wrote about this.

00:27:59.840 --> 00:28:03.080 align:middle line:84%
Plutarch in Ancient
Rome recorded these.

00:28:03.080 --> 00:28:06.290 align:middle line:84%
